6. write a program to reverse,slice,concatenate a string
#concatenate
x = "Python "
y = "is a"
z = "programming language"
print(x + y + z)

#reverse a string
sample= "Hi,How are you"[::-1]
print(sample)

#Slice
Text="wow,looking awesome"
print(Text[2:9])

Output:
--------
Python is aprogramming language
uoy era woH,iH
w,looki
